{"tid":2406112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解籤師傅陳天恩: 車公認為政府抗疫舉棋不定，封區勞民傷財。最好是仿傚內地封城、全民檢測和禁足28日才能完全控制疫情","createTime":"2021-02-13T02:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T08:21:58.000Z","uid":350584,"like":28,"dislike":297,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"fb029e39c2c6befe6034c9840571373f44b60738","tid":2406112,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:50:53.000Z","msg":"陳天恩又說，車公認為當局早前的封區措施勞民傷財，疫情只會無了期，最好是仿傚內地封城，全民檢測和禁足28日，才能完全控制疫情，經濟自然會復甦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575524-20210213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575524-20210213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=35dfd2c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575524-20210213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e9e064e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575524-20210213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"71179bd8226aa2160dcf2e5c435fb4072ea858ac","tid":2406112,"uid":350584,"like":61,"dislike":5,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"鄉議局主席劉業強在車公廟為香港求得第四十五籤的中籤，籤文是「下手須教一著先，世情局面苦徒然；積薪歷火非無事，識者能知火未燃」。<br />\n<br />\n解籤師傅陳天恩表示，車公認為政府抗疫措施舉棋不定，希望當局一氣呵成解決疫情，否則出現第5波、第6波疫情才知錯，經濟將更加會走下坡、市民會更惶恐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4541f8be5c4c848aebb6dbd250834fa007543a56","tid":2406112,"uid":374134,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:53:58.000Z","msg":"我嘅訴求就係想返工.